WEBVTT

01:51.080 --> 01:52.840
PATTIA CLUB

03:34.240 --> 03:36.080
I do not believe that my dream
is just an illusion,

03:37.320 --> 03:38.960
that there is no karma in this world.

03:39.720 --> 03:42.080
If the ocean is meant to spill,

03:42.160 --> 03:46.240
let the water of misery fill my heart.

03:46.320 --> 03:48.080
If far away I must go,

03:48.160 --> 03:50.080
the storms I must weather.

03:50.160 --> 03:51.920
All for freedom.

03:53.280 --> 03:54.320
By Xu Meng.

04:11.440 --> 04:12.800
What a shocker.

04:12.880 --> 04:15.320
All these smoke and mirrors
in superstition.

04:15.400 --> 04:18.839
In the end, it was all to run away
from debt collectors.

04:18.920 --> 04:21.680
We should be more rational.

04:24.720 --> 04:26.120
What's wrong?

04:26.200 --> 04:27.920
We solved the case. Why the long face?

04:29.480 --> 04:32.480
I'm wondering if this is the only answer.

04:32.560 --> 04:34.320
How many answers do you need?

04:34.400 --> 04:36.920
Even in a comic book,
they always say there's only one truth.

04:50.360 --> 04:52.560
What is going on? A grand reception?

04:55.880 --> 04:56.720
Captain.

04:56.800 --> 04:57.760
WEIYANG PUBLIC SECURITY BUREAU
NANSHAN BRANCH

04:57.840 --> 04:58.880
Let's go.

05:00.520 --> 05:01.560
Captain Feng.

05:02.920 --> 05:03.920
What's going on?

05:05.840 --> 05:09.160
You two solved a big case today.

05:11.200 --> 05:13.880
-We solved a case?
-How did you know we solved the case?

05:13.960 --> 05:15.600
I haven't even told you about it yet.

05:15.680 --> 05:18.840
Didn't you ask me
to ambush the pickpocket?

05:22.080 --> 05:23.960
He did see a briefcase

05:24.040 --> 05:26.720
with Qingsong Cement written on it.

05:26.800 --> 05:28.880
It was hidden inside Wu Shanlong's house.

05:29.520 --> 05:30.440
What was inside?

05:31.080 --> 05:33.440
Photocopies of the tender document
on Dongshan Mine.

05:33.520 --> 05:36.000
Does it mean the case is solved now?

05:36.080 --> 05:37.920
Wu Shanlong was the whistle-blower.

05:38.000 --> 05:41.200
Song Qingsong paid Director Li of the mine

05:41.280 --> 05:43.800
eight million yuan to win the bid.

05:43.880 --> 05:45.760
Director Li sure is cunning.

05:45.840 --> 05:46.920
He wants the best of both worlds.

05:47.000 --> 05:49.840
He sold the tender
to both Song Qingsong and Cripple Du.

05:49.920 --> 05:51.960
And in the end, they fought.

05:52.920 --> 05:55.680
I get it now. Director Li
conducted this whole farce.

05:55.760 --> 05:57.760
He said someone stole
the tender document from the mine.

05:57.840 --> 05:59.600
In reality, he was
just diverting attention.

05:59.680 --> 06:00.640
Exactly.

06:03.160 --> 06:05.760
Sir. We have good news too.

06:07.720 --> 06:09.600
Is it about
the missing father and daughter?

06:11.960 --> 06:14.080
They disappeared on purpose.
We have evidence.

06:16.280 --> 06:17.120
Good things come in pairs.

06:17.200 --> 06:19.280
When I see the chief next time,

06:19.360 --> 06:22.000
I'll put in a good word for you two.

06:22.080 --> 06:25.040
Sir. There's no rush for that.

06:25.640 --> 06:27.920
But my secondment ends tomorrow.

06:28.000 --> 06:29.360
I have to return to the police station.

06:29.440 --> 06:31.640
About my secondment evaluation report…

06:36.560 --> 06:38.480
Oh, He Yuanhang.

06:39.720 --> 06:40.720
You're crafty.

06:41.760 --> 06:44.880
Well, I have to bring something back
for that green-eyed colleague of mine.

06:44.960 --> 06:46.920
Before you return tomorrow,

06:47.000 --> 06:48.960
bring me the case summary report,

06:49.040 --> 06:51.440
and you'll have your evaluation report.

06:53.360 --> 06:55.280
Captain Feng, do I
have to write the report too?

06:55.880 --> 06:59.160
The quality of your report
will affect the quality of mine.

06:59.240 --> 07:00.320
What?

07:01.720 --> 07:02.560
All the best.

07:03.800 --> 07:05.520
But… Captain Feng.

07:05.600 --> 07:07.760
Tomorrow? I've stayed up late
for a few nights already.

07:13.680 --> 07:15.160
He. Go back and rest up.

07:15.240 --> 07:16.560
I'll write the report.

07:17.920 --> 07:19.160
It's okay.

07:19.240 --> 07:21.160
Working late is part and parcel
of being a criminal detective.

07:21.240 --> 07:22.600
You know what? Go back and sleep.

07:22.680 --> 07:24.080
Drop by my place tomorrow
at noon to check my report.

07:24.160 --> 07:26.240
You can also taste my wife's cooking.

07:26.320 --> 07:28.720
-She'll make noodles for you. See you.
-Okay.

07:29.840 --> 07:31.720
-Drive safely!
-Okay.

08:03.000 --> 08:05.560
Help yourself.

08:07.120 --> 08:07.960
Sir,

08:08.720 --> 08:10.800
I no longer eat coriander.

08:23.560 --> 08:24.640
Sir,

08:25.800 --> 08:27.640
you're now retired.

08:27.720 --> 08:29.400
Xiaohe has also grown up.

08:29.480 --> 08:31.880
Why don't you just enjoy your retirement?

08:34.520 --> 08:37.440
Are you telling me to give up?

08:39.360 --> 08:40.440
No.

08:41.039 --> 08:42.520
I'm telling you to accept
your current pace

08:42.600 --> 08:44.000
and you may continue to be useful.

08:44.080 --> 08:45.600
That's just giving up.

08:51.160 --> 08:52.960
Back then, you told me

08:53.840 --> 08:56.680
to let it go when it was time to do so
instead of dwelling on it.

08:56.760 --> 08:59.400
Otherwise, we would…

09:04.880 --> 09:05.720
Sir.

09:08.280 --> 09:10.040
Don't visit Yuanlongli anymore.

09:12.800 --> 09:14.280
I wanted to retire too back then.

09:15.000 --> 09:15.960
But you had to drag me in.

09:16.600 --> 09:18.360
Now, it's the other way round.

09:18.440 --> 09:19.880
Ran Fangxu.

09:19.960 --> 09:21.600
Just be frank with me.

09:21.680 --> 09:23.240
Are you going to pretend
for the rest of your life

09:23.320 --> 09:26.280
that the June 30th case never happened?

09:31.880 --> 09:33.400
I made a wrong call back then.

09:34.000 --> 09:34.960
That was on me.

09:35.760 --> 09:37.960
But it has been 18 years now.

09:38.040 --> 09:39.600
We've gone through every lead we had.

09:39.680 --> 09:41.080
There are no new leads.

09:41.160 --> 09:42.600
No new leads?

09:42.680 --> 09:43.880
Come here.

09:43.960 --> 09:45.800
-Sir.
-Come here.

09:46.440 --> 09:47.400
No new leads?

09:47.480 --> 09:48.880
No new leads? What is this?

09:49.720 --> 09:51.360
What is this?
What are these if not new leads?

09:51.440 --> 09:52.600
Sir!

09:54.440 --> 09:57.360
Why else do you think
I always visit Yuanlongli?

09:57.440 --> 10:00.160
Because I know
it has the most important lead.

10:00.240 --> 10:02.680
As long as Yuanlongli is still here,
the case can be solved.

10:02.760 --> 10:04.760
Let it go already, sir.

10:04.840 --> 10:07.160
No need to waste your life on one case.

10:07.240 --> 10:10.040
I can't! Just go away then.

10:10.120 --> 10:11.560
I'll just investigate it myself.

10:11.640 --> 10:12.480
Sir.

10:18.720 --> 10:19.560
Sir!

10:20.440 --> 10:22.640
YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

10:35.120 --> 10:36.480
MISSING PERSON

10:37.760 --> 10:40.760
Sir, what are you doing? Stop posting it.

10:41.840 --> 10:43.400
If you can insist on quitting,

10:43.480 --> 10:45.200
let me insist on investigating as well.

10:45.280 --> 10:46.520
We have nothing to do with each other.

10:49.840 --> 10:52.160
Your posters serve no purpose, sir.

10:53.520 --> 10:55.200
Just come back with me.

10:59.000 --> 11:00.160
Sir.

11:00.840 --> 11:01.680
Sir.

11:01.760 --> 11:04.200
Many things don't come with answers.

11:04.280 --> 11:05.560
I don't want answers.

11:05.640 --> 11:06.880
I want the truth.

11:06.960 --> 11:08.080
Let go. Let go of me.

11:08.160 --> 11:09.240
No!

11:09.320 --> 11:10.280
I won't unless you come back.

11:10.360 --> 11:11.560
I don't need you now. Let go.

11:11.640 --> 11:12.960
-No.
-Let…

11:18.560 --> 11:19.400
Who's there?

11:20.600 --> 11:22.720
Dad? What are you doing?

11:25.440 --> 11:26.280
Xiaohe.

11:32.600 --> 11:34.840
Xiaohe. Don't leave.

11:34.920 --> 11:36.920
Look. We're already here anyway.

11:37.000 --> 11:40.640
Maybe you, Uncle Ran, and I
can investigate this case together.

11:40.720 --> 11:42.640
I can't monitor you all the time.
I can't chain you to a post.

11:42.720 --> 11:43.880
I can't stop you.

11:43.960 --> 11:45.320
Whenever I go out,
you sneak into Yuanlongli.

11:45.400 --> 11:47.640
What if you fall sick again?

11:48.560 --> 11:50.480
Sick? Look at me.

11:50.560 --> 11:51.880
The very picture of health.

11:53.760 --> 11:57.800
Dad. I have work to do. Please

11:59.320 --> 12:01.040
go back with Uncle Ran.

12:01.760 --> 12:03.040
She's right.

12:03.120 --> 12:04.680
-Let's go, sir.
-Shut up.

12:05.600 --> 12:06.840
Xiaohe.

12:06.920 --> 12:08.720
You're here to find evidence

12:08.800 --> 12:11.200
to appeal against
Han Zi'ang's expulsion, aren't you?

12:11.280 --> 12:13.360
Since Uncle Ran and I are here,

12:13.440 --> 12:14.880
we can assist you.

12:14.960 --> 12:16.000
I don't need your help.

12:17.160 --> 12:19.440
Our investigation skills are exceptional.

12:19.520 --> 12:20.640
I don't need you.

12:20.720 --> 12:22.800
I can swear. I can swear

12:23.520 --> 12:26.320
that if we fail to find anything useful,

12:26.400 --> 12:27.520
we will leave right away.

12:27.600 --> 12:29.200
We won't disturb you when you work.

12:34.960 --> 12:36.920
What… What

12:37.760 --> 12:38.720
can you two do anyway?

12:39.840 --> 12:40.920
Right?

12:41.880 --> 12:43.480
I have no idea either.

12:43.560 --> 12:44.560
Don't play dumb.

12:48.360 --> 12:49.480
You know what?

12:49.560 --> 12:51.360
Take… Take the helmet for me.

12:53.320 --> 12:55.600
Stay here. Don't move. Come. Follow me.

12:56.920 --> 12:58.120
Where are you going?

12:58.200 --> 13:00.200
Just stay there. Don't move.

13:07.440 --> 13:08.600
MISSING PERSONS

13:12.680 --> 13:16.680
He Xiaohe. How can you believe
the words of a madman?

13:20.160 --> 13:22.160
-Run! Quick.
-What's going on?

13:22.240 --> 13:24.000
Quick! Quick!

13:24.080 --> 13:26.160
-It's dangerous. Move aside.
-Who's chasing after you?

13:26.240 --> 13:27.400
Careful.

13:27.480 --> 13:28.920
Dad! Who's pursuing you?

13:29.000 --> 13:30.320
-Careful.
-Dad!

13:39.400 --> 13:40.240
Dad!

13:47.760 --> 13:49.560
What are you trying to do?

13:49.640 --> 13:50.640
Who is pursuing you?

13:59.080 --> 14:02.480
Re-enactment is so effective.

14:02.560 --> 14:05.680
Dad. Can you stop messing around?

14:08.000 --> 14:09.800
This is called a re-enactment.

14:09.880 --> 14:12.480
It's Uncle Ran's expertise.

14:12.560 --> 14:14.040
Re-enactment?

14:15.400 --> 14:18.000
Put yourself in the shoes of Han Zi'ang

14:18.080 --> 14:19.960
and re-enact what he did.

14:20.040 --> 14:23.080
Then, find clues during the process.

14:23.160 --> 14:27.080
You're saying
that Han Zi'ang wasn't lying in ambush.

14:27.960 --> 14:29.240
Someone was pursuing him.

14:30.880 --> 14:33.640
That was why he hid in the cupboard.

14:35.960 --> 14:36.840
Where's your proof?

14:40.080 --> 14:42.440
Uncle Ran is back. He'll answer you.

14:43.080 --> 14:43.920
No need for that.

14:45.080 --> 14:47.960
Xiaohe is smart enough
to deduce it herself.

14:49.520 --> 14:50.880
Did you get it then?

15:39.120 --> 15:40.280
Help!

15:41.000 --> 15:43.800
Help! Help!

15:45.600 --> 15:47.080
Help!

15:49.880 --> 15:51.160
Help!

16:08.200 --> 16:09.200
I hear a ghost.

16:18.880 --> 16:19.800
Where is it?

16:20.400 --> 16:21.360
Over there.

16:36.200 --> 16:40.080
Han Zi'ang might have
been assaulted first.

16:40.160 --> 16:41.400
Then, he fled.

16:41.480 --> 16:42.600
Fearing assault,

16:42.680 --> 16:45.720
he acted out of self-defense
after he hid in the cupboard.

16:49.280 --> 16:50.160
Xiaohe.

16:51.160 --> 16:53.240
This is your logical deduction.

16:53.800 --> 16:56.920
You'll have to find the evidence yourself.

16:57.840 --> 16:59.480
Understood?

16:59.560 --> 17:00.920
You have to rely on yourself.

17:01.920 --> 17:05.280
Sir. You've seen how Xiaohe did just now.

17:05.359 --> 17:06.560
Yes.

17:07.520 --> 17:10.200
It exceeded my expectations.

17:10.280 --> 17:12.880
I know she is a capable officer,

17:13.760 --> 17:15.079
and I can't wait to see her
solve this case.

17:17.359 --> 17:19.960
Are you saying
that you still want to quit?

17:21.760 --> 17:22.599
Sir,

17:23.880 --> 17:26.280
I will wait for Xiaohe's
good news in Beijing.

17:27.560 --> 17:29.840
Then, I'll insert this case
into my teaching material.

17:31.000 --> 17:32.200
You're going back to Beijing?

17:32.880 --> 17:33.760
Yes.

17:50.600 --> 17:51.440
Dad.

17:52.520 --> 17:53.480
It'll be dawn soon.

17:54.840 --> 17:57.400
Uncle Ran has to catch the train.

18:14.760 --> 18:17.440
Let's go. I'll give you
a lift to the train station.

18:19.680 --> 18:20.560
Okay.

18:41.000 --> 18:42.680
AWARDED TO HE YUANHANG

18:42.760 --> 18:46.040
OUTSTANDING POLICE OFFICER
OF NANSHAN DISTRICT

18:48.320 --> 18:51.560
…THE STORMS I MUST WEATHER
ALL FOR FREEDOM. XU MENG

19:09.640 --> 19:13.040
YUANLONGLI JUNE 30TH CASE, SUMMARY REPORT

19:17.080 --> 19:19.080
On August 24th, 1995,

19:20.040 --> 19:22.360
Xu Zhihong, father, and Xu Meng, daughter,

19:22.440 --> 19:24.240
were involved in an accident on Mount Wu.

19:24.320 --> 19:26.680
Xu Zhihong suffered severe injuries

19:26.760 --> 19:27.600
-What's the matter?
-and had to seek

19:27.680 --> 19:28.840
long-term medical treatment.

19:29.360 --> 19:30.360
Dad!

19:30.920 --> 19:32.560
Dad! Dad!

19:33.160 --> 19:35.280
Save my dad. He fainted.

19:35.360 --> 19:37.360
Save my dad. Save my dad.

19:40.400 --> 19:43.200
Xu Meng pawned her assets
and took out loans

19:43.800 --> 19:45.200
to pay for her father's medical bills.

19:48.640 --> 19:52.920
IOU, XU MENG

20:00.960 --> 20:02.320
Didn't you say 8,000 yuan?

20:02.920 --> 20:03.960
How come there's only 6,000 yuan?

20:04.040 --> 20:06.280
You think I don't need
the handling fee? Huh?

20:08.200 --> 20:09.600
Don't just stand there.

20:11.120 --> 20:13.280
-Pay up now! Pay up!
-Pay up now!

20:13.360 --> 20:15.480
-Pay up!
-Pay up now! Pay up!

20:15.560 --> 20:17.160
-Pay up now!
-Pay up!

20:17.240 --> 20:18.240
-Pay up!
-Pay up!

20:18.320 --> 20:19.160
-Pay up now!
-Pay up!

20:19.240 --> 20:21.200
As the Xus accumulated debts,

20:21.280 --> 20:23.640
-debt collectors visited them more often.
-Pay up!

20:23.720 --> 20:24.720
They shouted threats,

20:25.320 --> 20:27.440
pushing the victims into desperation.

20:27.520 --> 20:28.840
-Pay up!
-Yes, pay up!

20:28.920 --> 20:30.520
-Pay up, Xu Meng!
-Xu Meng!

20:30.600 --> 20:33.040
-I know you're in there.
-Just come

20:34.520 --> 20:35.800
after me, you punks!

20:35.880 --> 20:37.440
Old cripple, come out now.

20:37.520 --> 20:39.800
-Get out now!
-Don't harass my daughter!

20:39.880 --> 20:41.040
-If you can stay in there,
-Stay put.

20:41.120 --> 20:42.920
-come out and pay up now.
-It's okay.

20:43.000 --> 20:44.120
-It's okay.
-Pay up!

20:44.200 --> 20:45.960
-Pay up!
-Bullying a girl now?

20:46.040 --> 20:47.920
-Come out now!
-Are you even men?

20:48.000 --> 20:48.920
Our investigation

20:49.520 --> 20:51.880
indicates that Xu Meng
defrauded many people

20:51.960 --> 20:54.200
by repeatedly mortgaging her property.

20:55.000 --> 20:57.160
They had the motive to run away

20:57.240 --> 21:00.680
from their debt collectors and pursuers.

21:06.000 --> 21:07.000
Mengmeng,

21:09.160 --> 21:10.520
death

21:12.200 --> 21:13.160
is

21:14.960 --> 21:17.400
our only solution.

21:22.400 --> 21:23.360
Dad,

21:24.760 --> 21:26.120
I don't want to die.

21:27.840 --> 21:29.240
Let's run away, okay?

21:30.520 --> 21:32.080
We'll disappear in Weiyang.

21:35.200 --> 21:36.440
Vanishing in Weiyang

21:37.120 --> 21:39.600
became their only way out.

21:44.720 --> 21:47.360
According to the testimony
of Du Mandun, a Yuanlongli resident,

21:48.040 --> 21:50.000
Xu Meng visited the New York Block

21:50.080 --> 21:53.560
to devise her escape route
before she executed her plan.

21:58.520 --> 22:01.080
Elevators are operated
by the same generic key.

22:01.160 --> 22:03.640
Having worked in Dajianchang
for many years,

22:04.240 --> 22:07.240
Xu Zhihong was familiar
with tools and could make keys.

22:08.560 --> 22:12.360
Additionally, the Xus
also picked the date carefully.

22:12.440 --> 22:13.640
They opted for a day when the residents

22:13.720 --> 22:16.160
would be watching the reunification
of Hong Kong broadcast.

22:16.240 --> 22:20.080
The absence of people on the street
facilitated their escape plan.

22:20.160 --> 22:22.960
At around 4:30 p.m., June 30th,

22:23.040 --> 22:24.520
Xu Meng carried Xu Zhihong on her back

22:24.600 --> 22:26.200
and arrived at Yuanlongli.

22:27.080 --> 22:29.000
At 4:38 p.m.,

22:29.080 --> 22:32.240
Xu Meng and Xu Zhihong
took the elevator to the 18th floor.

22:33.160 --> 22:34.920
Before they exited the elevator,

22:35.000 --> 22:37.360
Xu Zhihong pressed all the buttons
in the elevator.

22:49.880 --> 22:53.040
After they left the elevator,
they split up.

22:53.800 --> 22:56.760
When the elevator stopped briefly
on the 17th floor,

22:56.840 --> 22:59.640
Xu Meng went to 1813
and hung the black cloak.

23:00.520 --> 23:02.880
Xu Zhihong then unlocked
the door to the elevator shaft.

23:13.880 --> 23:15.400
They worked together

23:15.480 --> 23:17.360
and dragged two wooden planks
with their footprints

23:17.960 --> 23:19.560
to the top of the elevator.

23:25.960 --> 23:26.800
Preliminary analysis shows

23:26.880 --> 23:29.520
that Xu Meng's and Xu Zhihong's
footprints, handprints

23:29.600 --> 23:31.240
collected on the elevator roof,

23:31.320 --> 23:32.880
and even the handwriting in the letter,

23:32.960 --> 23:36.840
match the ones collected
in their place of residence.

23:37.840 --> 23:40.360
Dad. We must live on.

23:40.960 --> 23:41.880
Don't be scared.

24:00.800 --> 24:02.760
When the elevator stopped
on the first floor,

24:02.840 --> 24:05.560
the Xus unlocked
the elevator door from the shaft

24:05.640 --> 24:07.200
and arrived at the lobby
on the second floor.

24:32.560 --> 24:35.640
They took the eastern staircase
and headed to B1.

24:37.000 --> 24:39.080
It is connected
to the underground car park.

24:39.800 --> 24:41.680
When Xu Meng worked in Pattia,

24:41.760 --> 24:44.080
she got her hands on the keys
to the underground car park.

25:06.480 --> 25:10.080
YUANLONGLI UNDERGROUND PARKING LOT

25:38.640 --> 25:41.880
They took the car park exit
and left Yuanlongli.

25:42.440 --> 25:44.480
That route was not covered
by security cameras.

25:45.360 --> 25:48.920
The Xus mystified their disappearance

25:49.000 --> 25:51.120
so that rumors would spread.

25:51.200 --> 25:52.400
The superstitious beliefs

25:52.480 --> 25:55.040
would also deter their debt collectors
from coming closer,

25:55.120 --> 25:57.760
thereby giving up on pursuing them.

26:01.840 --> 26:05.120
In conclusion,
this is a premeditated, voluntary

26:05.200 --> 26:07.320
missing person case motivated
by the desire to evade debt collection.

26:16.280 --> 26:18.320
Should any request to locate them be made,

26:18.400 --> 26:20.440
we recommend requesting the city council

26:20.520 --> 26:22.640
to enlarge the search scope.

26:38.720 --> 26:40.640
WRITTEN BY, TIME

26:50.560 --> 26:52.560
Written by Ran Fangxu,

26:54.040 --> 26:55.040
He Yuanhang.

26:56.080 --> 26:57.880
WRITTEN BY: RAN FANGXU, HE YUANHANG
TIME: JULY 5TH, 1997

27:18.200 --> 27:19.200
Hi, Uncle Ran.

27:19.280 --> 27:21.200
-Hi, Xiaohe.
-You're here.

27:21.920 --> 27:22.880
Allow me to introduce him.

27:22.960 --> 27:25.200
Ran. R-A-N.

27:25.280 --> 27:26.480
Ran Fangxu.

27:26.560 --> 27:30.000
And this one is my wife,
Sun Yun. Director Sun.

27:30.080 --> 27:32.240
-Hi, Mrs. He.
-Hi, Ran.

27:33.200 --> 27:35.480
-This is for you.
-You didn't have to.

27:35.560 --> 27:38.240
Come in. Let me serve the noodles.

27:39.080 --> 27:40.040
Take the shoes.

27:41.480 --> 27:44.880
-Uncle Ran, your sandals.
-Thank you, Xiaohe. This is for you.

27:45.480 --> 27:47.000
What is that?

27:48.440 --> 27:49.720
Oh. A doll.

27:49.800 --> 27:51.400
Thank you, Uncle Ran.

27:54.360 --> 27:56.560
They both have something. Is this mine?

28:01.800 --> 28:04.480
A freebie when I bought
the gift for your wife.

28:05.400 --> 28:07.120
A freebie? I like it.

28:09.720 --> 28:10.560
It suits me.

28:11.240 --> 28:12.640
Come. Come.

28:18.880 --> 28:19.960
Here.

28:20.880 --> 28:21.720
Take a seat.

28:23.720 --> 28:25.680
Make sure you don't tell my wife later

28:25.760 --> 28:26.960
that I'm going back to the police station.

28:27.560 --> 28:28.960
But aren't you going back tomorrow?

28:29.800 --> 28:32.360
-You haven't told your wife?
-The noodles are ready.

28:33.920 --> 28:34.760
Come.

28:35.960 --> 28:37.240
How nice.

28:38.200 --> 28:41.720
Listen. My wife cooked
a whole table of food for you.

28:41.800 --> 28:42.680
Sorry for the hassle, Mrs. He.

28:42.760 --> 28:44.160
Not a hassle at all. Take a seat.

28:44.240 --> 28:45.200
Okay.

28:47.360 --> 28:48.560
It smells divine.

28:49.120 --> 28:52.640
Dad told me
Uncle Ran likes coriander best.

28:52.720 --> 28:54.720
I washed them all myself.

28:55.800 --> 28:57.120
Thank you, Xiaohe.

28:58.360 --> 28:59.640
Come. Let's have a toast.

28:59.720 --> 29:02.280
-Welcome to our humble abode, Ran.
-Thank you, Mrs. He.

29:02.360 --> 29:04.120
-You're welcome.
-Welcome.

29:08.240 --> 29:09.080
He Yuanhang.

29:09.880 --> 29:11.520
Are you hiding something from me?

29:14.560 --> 29:16.280
Why would I be hiding something from you?

29:17.360 --> 29:19.640
Didn't you say Ran was your apprentice?

29:19.720 --> 29:22.320
So isn't it a bit inappropriate for him
to call me Mrs. He?

29:24.720 --> 29:26.040
It sounds younger that way.

29:26.120 --> 29:28.000
Madam Sun sounds way older.

29:28.080 --> 29:31.040
Lie. Lie more.

29:31.760 --> 29:34.200
Ran is a top scorer from PPSUC.

29:34.280 --> 29:36.120
You're here for a secondment.

29:36.200 --> 29:38.120
There's no way he's your apprentice.

29:39.080 --> 29:40.320
Right, Ran?

29:45.920 --> 29:47.400
He

29:48.400 --> 29:49.600
is indeed my mentor.

29:53.120 --> 29:54.400
Did you hear that?

29:55.480 --> 29:57.720
Feng did this?

30:00.520 --> 30:02.240
-Eat more.
-Thank you, Mrs. He.

30:02.320 --> 30:05.560
You can hardly find a down-to-earth
young man nowadays.

30:06.160 --> 30:09.080
You're smart, capable,
and have the required qualification.

30:09.160 --> 30:12.120
I'm sure your workplace
will invest a lot in you.

30:13.240 --> 30:15.440
He will stay at the criminal department.

30:15.520 --> 30:19.000
Ran, you will support him, won't you?

30:21.840 --> 30:23.760
Actually, the criminal department
has a heavy workload.

30:23.840 --> 30:25.760
Even heavier than a bank.

30:25.840 --> 30:26.760
Xiaohe is still young.

30:26.840 --> 30:28.080
She needs her parents.

30:28.160 --> 30:29.800
Yes, Dad.

30:29.880 --> 30:31.280
I need my parents.

30:31.880 --> 30:32.720
For what?

30:35.360 --> 30:37.720
The biggest thing a father can do
for his children

30:37.800 --> 30:39.320
is to be a great role model,

30:39.400 --> 30:41.840
not to keep them company.

30:44.520 --> 30:45.720
Don't you agree, Ran?

30:47.800 --> 30:50.240
Yes. You're right.

30:50.320 --> 30:51.480
Oh, Ran.

30:52.200 --> 30:53.520
Are you single?

30:53.600 --> 30:55.760
I know many single women in my work.

30:55.840 --> 30:56.720
Do you want me to introduce
some of them to you?

30:56.800 --> 30:59.680
Uncle Ran doesn't need that.

30:59.760 --> 31:01.400
I know Ms. Qiao.

31:01.480 --> 31:03.080
She likes Uncle Ran.

31:03.160 --> 31:05.160
She's so pretty.

31:05.880 --> 31:08.280
Where does she work? She's quick.

31:09.200 --> 31:10.160
Mrs. He.

31:10.240 --> 31:12.040
I just arrived in Weiyang.

31:12.120 --> 31:13.160
I just want to focus on my work.

31:13.240 --> 31:15.400
I don't have time for anything else.

31:18.240 --> 31:19.800
Sir.

31:20.760 --> 31:22.920
How did the case report go?

31:23.520 --> 31:25.320
Oh. It's almost done.

31:25.400 --> 31:27.280
But I'm not so sure about certain details.

31:27.360 --> 31:28.880
Can you help me?

31:28.960 --> 31:31.640
-You can read it after the meal.
-It won't take long. Work comes first.

31:31.720 --> 31:32.880
Come. Take a look.

31:32.960 --> 31:34.840
We'll be back soon. Soon.

31:42.960 --> 31:44.760
Stop playing with it. Eat.

31:55.040 --> 31:58.120
SHE LEFT A LETTER. "I DO NOT BELIEVE
THAT MY DREAM IS JUST AN ILLUSION…"

32:03.600 --> 32:07.400
Where do you think they are right now?

32:11.280 --> 32:13.120
It's the first case of your life.

32:13.200 --> 32:16.360
Are you lamenting the fact
that you can't find them?

32:18.960 --> 32:22.360
No. Humans can adapt to many things.

32:22.960 --> 32:25.160
As long as they live a good life
where they are right now.

32:32.760 --> 32:35.160
It's good. Very thorough.

32:35.240 --> 32:37.640
I wouldn't have been able
to word it so vividly.

32:38.240 --> 32:40.680
Of course. I'm your mentor after all.

32:41.480 --> 32:43.320
Mr. He Yuanhang.

32:43.400 --> 32:45.440
Humility is often a virtue.

32:45.520 --> 32:47.120
Mr. Ran Fangxu.

32:47.200 --> 32:49.320
Humility in excess is arrogance.

32:54.320 --> 32:55.680
WRITTEN BY: RAN FANGXU, HE YUANHANG
TIME: JULY 5TH, 1997

33:01.120 --> 33:03.600
-What's wrong?
-The name sequence is wrong.

33:03.680 --> 33:05.120
No need for that.

33:05.200 --> 33:06.200
-He.
-It's fine.

33:06.280 --> 33:07.880
We must be truthful.

33:07.960 --> 33:10.240
I am being truthful. Listen.

33:10.320 --> 33:11.280
Investigation-wise,

33:11.360 --> 33:13.680
you are the main contributor
who solved this case.

33:13.760 --> 33:17.120
And in terms of your career,
you will stay in the criminal department.

33:17.200 --> 33:18.920
Whereas I will return
to the police station.

33:19.000 --> 33:20.520
-The sequence of our names
-Sir.

33:20.600 --> 33:21.600
-does not matter.
-Sir.

33:21.680 --> 33:23.440
Let me finish. It does not matter.

33:23.520 --> 33:25.800
Tomorrow, I'll take the evaluation
report Captain Feng gives me

33:25.880 --> 33:27.200
and return to the police station.

33:27.280 --> 33:30.920
I want to show Qu Dahai just how…

33:52.440 --> 33:55.000
-Why didn't you tell me?
-I tried.

33:55.080 --> 33:57.040
-What did you say?
-Sir.

34:09.880 --> 34:11.080
My wife is like this.

34:11.800 --> 34:13.440
She gets angry very fast,
but she also forgets about it very fast.

34:13.520 --> 34:14.880
She'll be fine in a few days.

34:16.120 --> 34:17.239
He.

34:18.520 --> 34:20.960
Have you ever considered staying?

34:23.400 --> 34:24.520
Of course I have.

34:25.120 --> 34:26.760
Why didn't you wait for me?

34:26.840 --> 34:28.800
I want to see Uncle Ran off too.

34:28.880 --> 34:31.560
Naughty girl! The floor is cold.
You came out without shoes.

34:31.639 --> 34:33.440
Wear your shoes. Come.

34:35.840 --> 34:37.159
You're here anyway.

34:37.239 --> 34:39.199
Why should I wear my shoes?

34:39.280 --> 34:41.440
Look at you. Your soles are dirty.

34:41.520 --> 34:43.360
When mom sees that, she'll scold you.

34:43.440 --> 34:44.760
Wash your feet when you go back.

34:44.840 --> 34:46.600
Okay. You have to teach me

34:46.679 --> 34:48.760
the 10th move of the evil-subduing
fist technique tonight.

34:48.840 --> 34:50.120
Of course.

34:51.719 --> 34:52.960
You see.

34:53.040 --> 34:55.719
I don't have a huge ambition.

34:55.800 --> 34:57.000
I understand.

34:57.080 --> 34:58.200
He.

35:00.960 --> 35:02.240
This isn't half bad either.

35:06.920 --> 35:08.240
Come. Let's see Uncle Ran off.

35:08.960 --> 35:11.400
Uncle Ran. Let me sing you a song.

35:11.480 --> 35:13.520
My class sings this song when someone

35:13.600 --> 35:15.320
-is transferring to another school.
-Sure.

35:16.160 --> 35:18.240
Traveling the world

35:18.320 --> 35:19.560
The journey

35:19.640 --> 35:20.640
Is endless

35:20.720 --> 35:22.440
Lost and aimless

35:22.520 --> 35:24.440
One village after another

35:24.520 --> 35:26.520
Staring at the setting sun

35:26.600 --> 35:27.560
Sinking

35:27.640 --> 35:28.640
And rising again

35:28.720 --> 35:29.640
The world

35:29.720 --> 35:30.640
Remains unchanged

35:30.720 --> 35:32.480
The time remains long

35:53.000 --> 35:55.160
You came all the way to Weiyang.

35:55.920 --> 35:59.040
And those old things in the bureau
won't even come to send you off.

35:59.120 --> 36:01.320
They are so heartless.

36:02.240 --> 36:04.320
Sir. They have work to do.

36:04.400 --> 36:06.000
They are in the special task force.

36:11.720 --> 36:13.640
WEIYANG STATION

36:13.720 --> 36:14.560
We're here.

36:19.160 --> 36:22.600
Xiaohe. Let me speak
to Uncle Ran privately.

36:40.920 --> 36:44.240
Have you ever considered staying?

36:46.920 --> 36:48.640
WEIYANG

36:52.120 --> 36:53.320
Maybe next time.

36:55.280 --> 36:56.160
I should go now.

37:04.880 --> 37:07.160
Xiaohe. I'm leaving now.

37:17.200 --> 37:18.720
She doesn't want you to leave either.

37:19.640 --> 37:20.920
But she's stubborn.

37:21.600 --> 37:22.880
She won't show it.

37:26.320 --> 37:27.240
Sir.

37:28.000 --> 37:28.920
Take care.

38:18.960 --> 38:20.680
Why did you leave so soon?

38:22.360 --> 38:24.600
You heartless creature.

38:24.680 --> 38:26.760
You won't even let me finish
what I want to say.

38:41.160 --> 38:44.560
Are you scolding the train or me? Sir.

39:01.360 --> 39:02.560
You decided to stay?

39:05.640 --> 39:06.480
Sir,

39:07.000 --> 39:08.440
you're right.

39:08.520 --> 39:09.840
I cannot run away from it forever.

39:10.480 --> 39:13.200
I'm staying to investigate
the June 30th case with you.

39:14.360 --> 39:16.480
You finally got it through
your thick head.

39:16.560 --> 39:19.040
I knew it. All these years in Beijing

39:19.120 --> 39:21.440
and you still care about this case. Right?

39:24.200 --> 39:26.320
Given your old age,

39:26.400 --> 39:28.240
without my assistance,

39:28.320 --> 39:30.120
you probably
won't be able to find anything.

39:30.960 --> 39:32.080
Good boy.

39:32.160 --> 39:33.840
You still care about me, after all.

39:34.960 --> 39:37.000
Xiaohe. Look.

39:37.080 --> 39:38.360
Guess who's back?

39:39.040 --> 39:41.640
Look. This is my apprentice.

39:41.720 --> 39:42.960
Ran Fangxu.

39:43.720 --> 39:47.120
When we work together, we are invincible.

39:47.760 --> 39:49.920
Peculiar cases or cold cases,

39:50.000 --> 39:51.400
they are nothing to us.

39:51.480 --> 39:54.960
Let alone a tiny Yuanlongli case. Right?

39:56.880 --> 39:57.720
He's my apprentice.

39:58.680 --> 39:59.520
My apprentice.

40:32.080 --> 40:33.200
Wait.

40:34.080 --> 40:36.240
I'm sure you've never left.

40:37.240 --> 40:40.000
When Mrs. Feng's grandson,
Ma Qiang's nephew,

40:40.080 --> 40:43.840
and Li Tieling's son
went missing in Yuanlongli,

40:43.920 --> 40:46.280
you helped me locate them.

40:47.840 --> 40:51.080
Sir. You got it wrong.

40:51.160 --> 40:52.720
I've been teaching in Beijing.

41:03.800 --> 41:04.920
This doesn't make sense.

41:06.160 --> 41:08.040
The train had already departed.

41:08.120 --> 41:10.520
You took the train and left
a long time ago.

41:10.600 --> 41:11.880
How did you return?

41:11.960 --> 41:14.080
How did the train return?
